r, LIME has been integrated with the proposed COV-ELM model to\ngenerate annotated CXR images. The annotations are based on the superpixels\nthat have contributed to distinguish between the different classes. It was\nobserved that the superpixels correspond to the regions of the human lungs that\nare clinically observed in COVID-19 and Pneumonia cases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Jul 2020 21:03:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 1 Aug 2020 09:33:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 15 Aug 2020 16:00:52 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 12 Mar 2021 16:26:10 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Fri, 6 Aug 2021 06:25:04 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Tue, 28 Sep 2021 05:31:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-29"}
