lity theory is used to construct phase\ndiagrams in parameter space characterizing where a switch-like emergence of\nintracellular oscillations can occur through a Hopf bifurcation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Jul 2020 05:33:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-20"}
